## Auto-fit text grid

````grid border=none
```cell
**Left column**

Each `cell` child is an independent body.
```

```cell
**Right column**

Without `cols`, the track count comes from the number of `cell` children.
```
````

## Steps

````steps
```step title="Install"
go install github.com/aXisho/cuemo@latest
```

```step title="Open a file"
cuemo README.cue.md
```

```step title="Edit and save"
The browser reloads automatically on every save.
```
````
